
# 🛒 E-Commerce REST API

![Java](https://img.shields.io/badge/Java-17-orange)
![Spring Boot](https://img.shields.io/badge/SpringBoot-Framework-brightgreen)
![MySQL](https://img.shields.io/badge/Database-MySQL-blue)
![JWT](https://img.shields.io/badge/Auth-JWT-yellow)
![Maven](https://img.shields.io/badge/Build-Maven-red)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-lightgrey)

A **secure and scalable RESTful backend application** for an e-commerce platform built using **Java and Spring Boot**.
The system provides APIs for **user authentication, product management, shopping cart operations, and order processing** while following **REST architecture and clean layered design**.

---

# 📌 Project Highlights

* 🔐 **JWT Authentication** with Spring Security
* 👥 **Role-Based Access Control** (Admin & Customer)
* 🛍 **Product Management System**
* 🛒 **Shopping Cart Functionality**
* 📦 **Order Processing & Tracking**
* 🧱 **Layered Architecture** (Controller → Service → Repository)

---

# 🏗 System Architecture

```
Controller Layer
       │
       ▼
Service Layer
       │
       ▼
Repository Layer
       │
       ▼
Database (MySQL)
```

