# 🔗 Sample API Endpoints

### Authentication

```
POST /api/auth/register
POST /api/auth/login
```

### Products

```
GET    /api/products
POST   /api/products
PUT    /api/products/{id}
DELETE /api/products/{id}
```

### Cart

```
POST   /api/cart/add
GET    /api/cart
DELETE /api/cart/{productId}
```

### Orders

```
POST /api/orders
GET  /api/orders/user
```

